<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.3">
<l>uṭaiyāṉai yolinī rulakaṅkaḷ paṭaittāṉai</l>
<l>viṭaiyāṉō ṭavaṉṟu viṟalāḻivi caittāṉai</l>
<l>yaṭaiyārteṉ ṉilaṅkai yaḻittāṉai yaṇiyaḻuntūr</l>
<l>uṭaiyāṉai yaṭiyē ṉaṭaintuyn tupōṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having taken refuge in the possessor [of all],</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who created the worlds with roaring sea,</l>
<l>The one who once hurled his heroic disc so that the one with the bull fled,</l>
<l>The one who destroyed his enemies’ Laṅkā to the south,</l>
<l>The possessor of beautiful Aḻuntūr, I, his servant, was ultimately saved.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
